name: AnimeChar (with Clothings) - Makai Tenshi Mix | Sei Tenshi Djibril (聖天使ジブリール)
description:
** I am new on training clothings models. So the clothings Lora may be updated (or discontinued) at anytime.


Greetings to all,

We are delighted to inform you about the release of our new series, Makai Tenshi Mix, which is now available on AnimeChar. This series brings together a unique combination, serving as a model that I personally created for my own enjoyment, and it marks my first attempt at designing clothing for a specific character.

In this series, we would like to introduce our newly trained Lora model of Sei Tenshi Djibril (聖天使ジブリール), a character in 魔界天使ジブリール.

Trigger words:

Character: manabe_rika, blue_hair, green eyes

Clothings: angelMagicalClothes, sailor_collar, crop_top, one-piece_swimsuit, elbow_gloves, gloves, puffy_sleeves

Other suggested: halo, wings

You may buy me a drink to support my work ^v^ : https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ryalandai
My instagram for ai painting and model updates: https://www.instagram.com/rya.land.ai
Also, you welcome to give 5 stars to the model.

Please check "About this version" to know more details about the model version and included characters. The model base is Anything v4.0.
